{"id": 392, "genre": 1000, "title": "12个现象告诉你，最近到底有多流行健身？", "description": "人鱼线是新美德，健身宣言是新鸡汤。", "record_count": 7883, "comment_count": 34, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703130124K0dwE35YTXc8JC4r.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-06-11T00:00:13Z", "questions": [{"id": 283, "title": "12个现象告诉你，最近到底有多流行健身？", "content": "12个现象告诉你，最近到底有多流行健身？\r\n", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 2494, "content": "朋友圈里总有人晒TA的跑步路线", "image": "img/option/option/20160703125958ltd9Z8KWSTyUPmxY.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 2495, "content": "朋友圈总是有人晒健身房的照片", "image": "img/option/option/2016070218312931vSO2P96ZKi5hIG.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 2496, "content": "朋友圈总是有人晒一双跑鞋的照片", "image": "img/option/option/201607031259599pGKPMNlXZOStEa3.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 2497, "content": "朋友圈总是有人在晒运动后的自己", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183256H2kUQc4hBl0yEbdC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 2498, "content": "总是看到有人在微博转发健身动作", "image": "img/option/option/20160703125959VpTdU6FBcOAfQL3W.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 2499, "content": "身边总有几个朋友在上私教课", "image": "img/option/option/20160703125959oQ7mE5tNL1fnsXM4.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 2500, "content": "讨厌的明星一旦说有腹肌，就让人立刻好感度上升", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183257x6h9HNlusVmed4CM.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 2501, "content": "可爱的明星一旦说有腹肌，就更让人刮目相看", "image": "img/option/option/201607031300000lzvf1XbqaAgPZK7.JPEG", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 2502, "content": "还有人为了微信运动排名靠前而疯狂走路", "image": "img/option/option/20160703130000fVwtZz7SBR6pxAro.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 2503, "content": "知乎首页每天都有健身相关的问题", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183257TqbJLXA8UK2k6aDj.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select":